title: Swivl

creator: Swivl
descriptionHtml:
Getting Started
1. Open this app and connect to your Swivl robot.
2. Login to your Swivl account
3. Connect all the Markers you have to capture or stream multiple audio channels.

Recording
Record and upload video to your Swivl account. From there you can easily watch the video, post questions, and securely share with a peer or coach to get objective feedback.

Streaming
Launch your favorite live streaming app, like Zoom, to stream content to remote students. The Markers have wireless microphones and the robot will continue to rotate to track you as you move around.

Compatibility
-Works with your C Series and CX Robots
-Connects up to 5 Markers (microphones) for independent audio channels

Links:
Swivl+ Student: https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.swivl.plus
Swivl Screencast: swivl.com/screen-recording
Swivl Web: cloud.swivl.com
Help: swivl.com/setup
descriptionShort: This is the official companion app for your Swivl robot.

appDetails.recentChangesHtml:
- New Capture screen
- Bug fixes
